al-hikmah","tag-agreed-upon-muttafaqun-alayhi","tag-companions-sahaba","tag-debt-al-dayn","tag-forbearance-al-hilm","tag-harshness","tag-loans","tag-manners-adab","tag-rights-al-huquq","tag-speech-al-qawl"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-al8","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":3439,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/06\/27\/sabr-tyrants\/","url_meta":{"origin":39750,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Tyrants: The Prophet orders patience with unjust rulers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, after me there will be undue favoritism and matters you will reject.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what do you order us to do if we reach that time?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cFulfill\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7844,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/06\/no-hasad-but-two-cases\/","url_meta":{"origin":39750,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Admiration: No envy except for charity, knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 6, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no envy but in two cases: a man whom Allah has given wealth and he spends it rightly, and a man whom Allah has given wisdom and he judges and teaches with it.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13877,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/02\/love-ansar-companions-faith\/","url_meta":{"origin":39750,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ansar: Love for companions is part of faith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 2, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Bara' reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNone loves the Ansar but a believer, and none hates them but a hypocrite. Whoever loves them, Allah will love him. Whoever hates them, Allah will hate him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3783, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 75 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7967,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/11\/encouraged-sahabah-help\/","url_meta":{"origin":39750,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Help: The Prophet encourages companions to help the needy","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 11, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: If a beggar or a needy person came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, he would say to his companions, \u201cIntercede and you will be rewarded; let Allah decree upon the tongue of his messenger what he wills.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5681, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11519,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/18\/do-not-curse-insult-sahabah\/","url_meta":{"origin":39750,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: Do not curse companions of the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not insult my companions. If one of you were to spend the likes of mount Uhud in gold, it would not reach a small portion of theirs or even half of that.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3673,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25470,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/29\/using-vessels-kuffar-mushrikin\/","url_meta":{"origin":39750,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Utensils: Using the dishware of idolaters if necessary","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 29, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Imran ibn Hussein reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and his companions performed ablution from the waterskin of an idolatrous woman. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 337, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 682 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u0650\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062d\u064f\u0635\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0646\u064d \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u065